<subSubSection id="C37B6522263A9C31A1FF3348FBF116B3" pageId="5" pageNumber="66" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BDE36A9263A9C31A1FF3348FBF116B3" blockId="5.[136,1452,1745,1983]" pageId="5" pageNumber="66">
We consider 
<taxonomicName id="4C614D2A263A9C31A07E3348FE77165E" authorityName="Gagnepain" authorityYear="1907" box="[265,384,1853,1875]" class="Liliopsida" family="Burmanniaceae" genus="Burmannia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Dioscoreales" pageId="5" pageNumber="66" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="luteoalba">
<emphasis id="B915EABB263A9C31A07E3348FE77165E" box="[265,384,1853,1875]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="66">B. luteoalba</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as doubtfully known from 
<collectingCountry id="F3767639263A9C31A3E7334BFD01165F" box="[656,758,1853,1875]" name="Cambodia" pageId="5" pageNumber="66">Cambodia</collectingCountry>
. This species is listed by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF04B58263A9C31A284334BFB6A165F" author="Cho, S. H. &amp; Chhang, P. &amp; Kim, Y. D." box="[1011,1181,1853,1875]" pageId="5" pageNumber="66" refId="ref4103" refString="Cho, S. H., Chhang, P. &amp; Kim, Y. D. (2016) A checklist for the seed plants of Cambodia. National Institute of Biological Resources, Ministry of Environment, Incheon, 272 pp." type="book" year="2016">
Cho 
<emphasis id="B915EABB263A9C31A5543348FBA1165E" box="[1059,1110,1853,1875]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="66">et al.</emphasis>
(2016)
</bibRefCitation>
most likely on the basis of 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF04B58263A9C31A1CA3317FE80167A" author="Gagnepain, F." box="[189,375,1889,1911]" pageId="5" pageNumber="66" pagination="459 - 465" refId="ref4322" refString="Gagnepain, F. (1907) Quelques Burmannia asiatiques nouveaux de l'Herbier du Museum. Bulletin de la Societe Botanique de France 54 (5): 459 - 465. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 00378941.1907.10831293" type="journal article" year="1907">Gagnepain’s (1907</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF04B58263A9C31A0F43317FE43167B" author="Gagnepain, F." box="[387,436,1889,1911]" pageId="5" pageNumber="66" pagination="18 - 25" refId="ref4364" refString="Gagnepain, F. (1908) Burmanniacees. In: Lecomte, H. &amp; Gagnepain, F. (Eds.) Flore generale de l'Indo-Chine, vol. 6. Masson &amp; Cie, Paris, pp. 18 - 25." type="book chapter" year="1908">1908</bibRefCitation>
) citations of the 
<typeStatus id="54DA880B263A9C31A32B3314FD72167B" box="[604,645,1890,1911]" pageId="5" pageNumber="66">type</typeStatus>
collection of this species as from “ 
<collectingCountry id="F3767639263A9C31A2953317FBBD167B" box="[994,1098,1889,1911]" name="Cambodia" pageId="5" pageNumber="66">Cambodia</collectingCountry>
: Phu Quoc island”; meanwhile, Phu Quoc island is currently a Vietnamese territory. Apart from the specimens from Phu Quoc, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF04B58263A9C31A53A33F3FB231697" author="Zhang, D." box="[1101,1236,1925,1947]" pageId="5" pageNumber="66" refId="ref6052" refString="Zhang, D. (1999) Systematics of Burmannia L. (Burmanniaceae) in the Old World. Unpublished PhD thesis, The University of Hong Kong, 331 pp." type="book" year="1999">Zhang (1999)</bibRefCitation>
indicated a specimen 
<emphasis id="B915EABB263A9C31A1CA33DFFEB616B2" box="[189,321,1961,1982]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="66">Godefroy 920</emphasis>
(P: P02086282) collected in 
<collectingCountry id="F3767639263A9C31A32D33DFFD4816B3" box="[602,703,1961,1983]" name="Cambodia" pageId="5" pageNumber="66">Cambodia</collectingCountry>
, which identification is uncertain.
</paragraph>
